Slugslinger turned ungracefully due to dammage, and was suprised by the
Autobot. This suprised resulted in a quick pull of Caliburst, which
burst out to streams of 25 machine gun bullets towards the Autobot. "Is
it good to see you Quake." SLugslinger said, unaware of Tremor's name
change.

Cliffjumper strugled to look up, and saw the Autobot symbol through
blurry vision, "Theyr Autobots." he whispered.
